thread.title: BRIEF-Beijing Wandong Medical Technology sees FY 2017 net profit up 50 pct to 55 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Beijing Wandong Medical Technology sees FY 2017 net profit up 50 pct to 55 pct

organizations.name: beijing wandong medical technology co ltd

text:
Jan 19(Reuters) - Beijing Wandong Medical Technology Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 50 percent to 55 percent, or to increase 36 million yuan to 40 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 71.5 million yuan
* The reasons for the forecast are increased sales and contribution from rental income Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/17QgnM Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
